    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and taken care of, so it runs like a dream. It's perfect for someone looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road. I've had zero issues with it, just looking to pass it on to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
