    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a precise six-speed manual and a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. Essential preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its condition, the suspension remains sharp with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the chassis dynamics remain true to its M-division heritage.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
