    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for a new owner to take the wheel. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
